A Gnome Power of inventions and good luck that lives on Bytopia. In the gnomish realm of the Golden Hills, he keeps a workshop known simply as the Workshop. He likes to go to Olympus once in a while, though; he has recently camped in the workshop of Hephaestus.
On Toril, the spells of his priests are actually granted by Gond. 

